transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Sir, good morning.
Customer: Good morning.
Executive: Ji, Bhabhi baat kar raha tha India Mart se. Sir, woh date aapne kya bataya tha ki kab tak resolve ho jayega, bhool gaya tha.
Customer: Kaun kaun bol raha hai?
Executive: Main baat kar raha hu India Mart se.
Customer: Boliye na Bhabhi ji.
Executive: Ji, woh date aapne kya bataya tha mujhe kab tak resolve ho jayega woh ek baar bata dijiye mention karna bhool gaya tha main.
Customer: Main aisa kal toh bataya tha main do teen din mein aane wala hu.
Executive: Achcha matlab 28 29 tak.
Customer: Somwar Monday ka rakho na.
Executive: Somwar tak resolve hoga.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Chaliye theek hai.
